The paper deals with the relationship between logical and process specifications, which suggests that it could belong to categories related to logic (cs.LO), process algebra (cs.PL), and labeled transition systems (cs.LT). Additionally, the paper discusses simulation relations, which are often used in software engineering (cs.SE) and formal languages (cs.FL).
